WEBVTT

00:00:50.780 --> 00:00:55.740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

00:00:56.820 --> 00:00:59.780
=Episode 18=
=The Other Me in the World=

00:01:04.200 --> 00:01:05.160
Chen Miaomiao,

00:01:06.800 --> 00:01:07.680
I'm warning you.

00:01:08.680 --> 00:01:09.880
This is the last time.

00:01:12.440 --> 00:01:13.280
Brother.

00:01:13.760 --> 00:01:14.790
What do you mean by that?

00:01:15.480 --> 00:01:16.320
I don't get it.

00:01:17.640 --> 00:01:18.880
The wounds on Ding Daang.

00:01:21.480 --> 00:01:23.440
Do you really think I don't know?

00:01:23.440 --> 00:01:24.640
You're the one who pushed her.

00:01:25.960 --> 00:01:26.800
Yes.

00:01:27.440 --> 00:01:28.400
I pushed her.

00:01:29.200 --> 00:01:30.280
She took Hu Yitong away.

00:01:30.280 --> 00:01:31.720
Now she's trying to take you too.

00:01:32.600 --> 00:01:33.480
I hate her.

00:01:40.280 --> 00:01:41.160
You've lost it.

00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:43.520
Yeah, I've lost it.

00:01:44.080 --> 00:01:44.920
What about you?

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:46.660
Have you forgotten

00:01:46.660 --> 00:01:48.240
how heartless you were when you left her?

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:01.360
You promised you'd help me.

00:02:01.360 --> 00:02:02.520
But look at you now.

00:02:02.920 --> 00:02:04.520
All you care is Ding Daang.

00:02:07.380 --> 00:02:08.240
Do you even realize

00:02:08.240 --> 00:02:09.080
what you're doing?

00:02:09.090 --> 00:02:09.940
Don't touch me.

00:02:10.680 --> 00:02:11.520
Don't you dare.

00:02:28.840 --> 00:02:31.800
Chen Aming.

00:02:33.600 --> 00:02:35.280
Chen Aming.

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:38.160
Is that really true?

00:02:44.920 --> 00:02:46.200
I'm Aming.

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:50.600
I'm Chen Aming.

00:03:14.280 --> 00:03:15.680
Get out!

00:03:28.240 --> 00:03:29.400
I'm Yu Kun.

00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:03.560
What happened?

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:10.200
I accidentally

00:04:10.200 --> 00:04:11.480
ran into a tricycle today.

00:04:12.520 --> 00:04:13.360
It's nothing serious.

00:04:47.240 --> 00:04:49.000
You don't think my injury's fake, do you?

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:11.120
What are you doing?

00:05:32.360 --> 00:05:33.280
I'm thirsty.

00:05:33.960 --> 00:05:34.800
I want some water.

00:05:54.800 --> 00:05:56.480
The ice pack doesn't feel cold anymore.

00:05:57.120 --> 00:05:58.080
Grab a new ice pack.

00:06:15.680 --> 00:06:16.520
Does it still hurt?

00:06:23.280 --> 00:06:24.400
About Miaomiao's situation,

00:06:26.240 --> 00:06:27.840
I want to apologize to you for her.

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:30.280
These past few years,

00:06:32.760 --> 00:06:34.000
I've really neglected her.

00:06:38.120 --> 00:06:39.600
Then treat her better from now on.

00:06:46.680 --> 00:06:47.640
I think

00:06:49.120 --> 00:06:50.280
I'm quite a loser.

00:07:12.240 --> 00:07:13.080
Aming,

00:07:16.640 --> 00:07:17.800
we don't have to

00:07:17.800 --> 00:07:19.360
get a perfect score every time.

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:24.640
As long as we're still alive,

00:07:26.240 --> 00:07:27.280
we haven't really lost.

00:07:59.440 --> 00:08:00.560
I don't blame Miaomiao.

00:08:06.200 --> 00:08:08.520
I can feel how much she's hurting,

00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:10.400
lost and confused.

00:08:13.440 --> 00:08:14.480
She shoved me.

00:08:15.680 --> 00:08:18.720
Because she was venting her anger
at Hu Yitong

00:08:20.520 --> 00:08:21.880
and her frustration toward you

00:08:21.880 --> 00:08:23.080
all on me.

00:08:26.400 --> 00:08:27.240
Just like,

00:08:29.320 --> 00:08:31.640
I often feel you're not really Aming.

00:08:36.080 --> 00:08:38.640
Because he'd never treat her that way.

00:08:45.100 --> 00:08:48.060
(Name: Yu Kun, Gender: Male, Age: 28)

00:08:50.700 --> 00:08:51.950
(Chief complaint: Mood swings,
sleep disorder,)

00:08:51.950 --> 00:08:53.180
(ongoing for 2 years,
worsened in the past month.)

00:08:56.060 --> 00:08:59.300
(Posted intense remarks,
causing loss of client partnerships.)

00:08:59.300 --> 00:09:01.140
(Feels physically heavy,
suicidal intention.)

00:09:01.160 --> 00:09:03.200
Zhou Haoran, what on earth are you doing?

00:09:04.120 --> 00:09:05.040
Maimai, calm down.

00:09:05.680 --> 00:09:06.800
We're handling this matter.

00:09:06.920 --> 00:09:07.840
Are you?

00:09:08.240 --> 00:09:09.200
Handling what exactly?

00:09:09.800 --> 00:09:11.600
Are you toying with Ding Daang's life?

00:09:12.200 --> 00:09:13.000
Calm down.

00:09:14.000 --> 00:09:14.880
Anger ages you faster.

00:09:15.000 --> 00:09:17.080
I don't care about your lousy plans.

00:09:17.720 --> 00:09:19.760
I just want Ding Daang to be alright.

00:09:20.600 --> 00:09:21.440
Come on.

00:09:22.600 --> 00:09:24.050
Seeing you like this makes me uneasy.

00:09:24.880 --> 00:09:26.160
You really have no idea.

00:09:27.320 --> 00:09:28.240
To me, Ding Daang

00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:30.120
is much more than just a friend.

00:09:33.280 --> 00:09:34.680
Back then, my brother was in debt.

00:09:35.280 --> 00:09:36.320
I worked to pay it off.

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:37.640
Every morning when I woke up,

00:09:37.640 --> 00:09:38.960
all I did was work to make money.

00:09:38.960 --> 00:09:40.600
I didn't even have time to cry.

00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:43.720
Without Ding Daang,

00:09:45.360 --> 00:09:46.640
I wouldn't be who I am today.

00:09:51.400 --> 00:09:52.240
I know.

00:09:53.440 --> 00:09:55.000
Yu Kun is also someone I deeply value.

00:09:55.960 --> 00:09:57.000
He made me realize

00:09:57.680 --> 00:09:59.320
how much a career matters to a man.

00:10:12.160 --> 00:10:13.240
But you changed me.

00:10:14.280 --> 00:10:15.120
Maimai.

00:10:21.160 --> 00:10:22.000
Because of you,

00:10:24.520 --> 00:10:26.000
I want to believe in love again.

00:10:28.280 --> 00:10:29.120
Zhou Haoran,

00:10:32.440 --> 00:10:33.760
do you dare to be with me?

00:10:37.000 --> 00:10:41.830
♪Memories linger softly in my dreams♪

00:10:43.120 --> 00:10:48.610
♪Who dispelled the depression
of yesterday?♪

00:11:17.960 --> 00:11:19.160
Chen Aming!

00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:20.400
I'm thirsty.

00:11:20.720 --> 00:11:21.600
I want...

00:11:21.600 --> 00:11:23.280
the fruit tea you made for me yesterday.

00:11:24.120 --> 00:11:24.960
Sure.

00:11:25.880 --> 00:11:27.320
And I want a chestnut cake too.

00:11:27.320 --> 00:11:29.120
The kind fresh out of Suga Love's oven.

00:11:29.480 --> 00:11:30.320
Got it.

00:11:34.480 --> 00:11:35.600
Chen Aming!

00:11:36.200 --> 00:11:37.840
Come here and help me beat this level.

00:11:37.840 --> 00:11:39.200
I can't get through it.

00:11:40.320 --> 00:11:41.200
Ding Daang,

00:11:41.440 --> 00:11:42.280
your leg is injured.

00:11:42.280 --> 00:11:43.560
But your hands still work fine.

00:11:52.760 --> 00:11:53.800
The fruit tea's ready.

00:12:00.520 --> 00:12:02.240
I'll go buy you a cake.

00:12:16.400 --> 00:12:17.240
Careful, it's hot.

00:12:29.240 --> 00:12:30.560
Looks like we're about to success.

00:12:30.650 --> 00:12:31.520
Success?

00:12:31.520 --> 00:12:32.880
What does success even mean?

00:12:32.960 --> 00:12:34.840
You just want him to love you, don't you?

00:12:35.520 --> 00:12:37.360
If he'd rather die just to forget you,

00:12:37.360 --> 00:12:39.120
why not let him go?

00:12:39.800 --> 00:12:41.880
His life matters more than anything.

00:12:42.400 --> 00:12:43.800
Ding Daang wants you.

00:12:45.160 --> 00:12:46.040
Not me.

00:12:47.360 --> 00:12:48.640
But what makes you think

00:12:49.960 --> 00:12:51.840
you deserve her heart?

00:12:52.440 --> 00:12:53.440
While I

00:12:54.400 --> 00:12:56.760
only get to live in your shadow.

00:13:01.120 --> 00:13:02.160
Chen Aming.

00:13:30.600 --> 00:13:37.600
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

00:13:42.000 --> 00:13:49.360
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

00:13:53.810 --> 00:13:55.750
♪They say♪

00:13:56.160 --> 00:14:04.540
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

00:14:05.060 --> 00:14:08.040
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

00:14:08.260 --> 00:14:14.210
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

00:14:15.590 --> 00:14:21.350
♪I've already lost you♪

00:14:21.350 --> 00:14:26.830
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

00:14:27.130 --> 00:14:33.080
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

00:14:33.080 --> 00:14:37.860
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

00:14:38.970 --> 00:14:43.000
♪The past will always pass♪

00:14:43.330 --> 00:14:50.910
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

00:14:51.380 --> 00:14:54.630
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

00:14:55.190 --> 00:15:00.840
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

00:15:03.300 --> 00:15:06.830
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

00:15:06.830 --> 00:15:13.090
♪But sadly, it's not you♪